#. [campaign], id=vendraxis_prophecy
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/_main.cfg:50
msgid ""
"Join a saurian adventure of Zanza and her tribe. She will leave the swamps "
"and travel into the mountains. Here she will meet new enemies and friends. "
"All that just to fullfill an old prophecy.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Únete a la aventura sauria de Zanza y su tribu. Ella abandonará los pantanos "
"y viajará hacia las montañas. Allí conocerá nuevos enemigos y aliados. Todo "
"para cumplir una antigua profecía.\n"
"\n"

