#. [then]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:24
msgid ""
"I can feel a dark presence in this thing. It looks similar to the urn we "
"found earlier. I think we should destroy it."
msgstr ""
"Puedo sentir una presencia oscura en esto. Se parece mucho a la urna que "
"encontramos antes. Creo que deberíamos destruirla."

#. [else]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:27
msgid "What is that?"
msgstr "¿Qué es eso?"

#. [else]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:28
msgid ""
"That is... That looks quite similar to the urn from the snow pass. I feel a "
"dark presence in it. I think we should destroy it."
msgstr ""
"Eso es... Se parece mucho a la urna del paso nevado. Siento una presencia "
"oscura en ella. Creo que deberíamos destruirla."

#. [option]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:47
msgid "Let's get rid of this urn."
msgstr "Deshagámonos de esta urna."

#. [option]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:67
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:101
msgid "Maybe not..."
msgstr "Tal vez no..."

#. [option]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:90
msgid "Let's get rid of it."
msgstr "Deshagámonos de ella."

#. [then]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:129
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:145
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:161
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:177
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/macros/utils_campaign.cfg:193
msgid "Skalith Hyksa!!!"
msgstr "¡Skalith Hyksa!!!"

#. [part]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/scenarios/01_Practice_in_the_Swamps.cfg:19
msgid ""
"One year before the fall of Saurgath, a small hunting band gathered in the "
"Swamp of Dread."
msgstr ""
"Un año antes de la caída de Saurgath, un pequeño grupo de cazadores se "
"reunió en el Pantano del Terror."

#. [part]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/scenarios/01_Practice_in_the_Swamps.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Zanza, a young saurian huntress, had been chosen to lead the next hatching. "
"To prove herself ready for the trials ahead, her skills were tested."
msgstr ""
"Zanza, una joven cazadora sauria, había sido elegida para liderar la próxima "
"eclosión. Para demostrar que estaba lista para las pruebas que venían, "
"pusieron a prueba sus habilidades."

#. [part]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/scenarios/01_Practice_in_the_Swamps.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Thhsthss, one of the elders, watched closely. He sought to see whether she "
"was the one foretold in his prophecies."
msgstr ""
"Thhsthss, uno de los ancianos, observaba con atención. Buscaba saber si ella "
"era la elegida de sus profecías."

#. [objectives]
#: Vendraxis_Prophecy/scenarios/01_Practice_in_the_Swamps.cfg:36
msgid "Defeat all animals"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los animales"

